  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 387.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "To-- no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "To [NON-ENGLISH] and a couple of other places, we distributed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], [NON-ENGLISH], and what's one near [NON-ENGLISH], one-- one near [NON-ENGLISH]?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Something-- one-- and maybe [NON-ENGLISH], right near it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was-- I was in that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think it was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we're different-- you know, the kibbutz are going to take so many.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We're there on-- for the what they call a [NON-ENGLISH], forming a [NON-ENGLISH], forming a formation, the essence of a [NON-ENGLISH] today.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then they established I think in '49 Kibbutz Lavi.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Kibbutz Lavi now have 600 people on them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they are near Tiberias.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It's a big kibbutz.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They also have several-- several-- they have a hotel of several big apartment building which are like hotels and a big dining hall.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That's one of their businesses.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they have different people there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They have-- they have about 600 people there all together now.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But the essence was the people coming from-- of course, other Israelis joined them and others joined them eventually.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But they had-- the essence came from England, from the various hakhshara in different parts of England, and then landed up in Kibbutz Lavi.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So-- but then, after a couple of weeks I-- I was there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I wanted to join up with the Air Force.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had a dream of being a pilot.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I want to join the Air Force.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [NON-ENGLISH] they had then-- they had then the [NON-ENGLISH], the pilot's called it [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It wasn't a pilot-- it wasn't [INAUDIBLE] flying done, just a couple of houses, which was called the pilot school, where the people were lined up in preparation to being sent out of the country.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was no training in Israel for pilots at that point.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
